    "title": "Urgent Opening Real Estate Agent at RMZ Corp International Enterprises",
    "description": "We at RMZ Corp International Enterprises are looking for an experienced Real Estate Agent based out of Jodhpur. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout RMZ Corp International Enterprises:\nRMZ Corp International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with RMZ Corp International Enterprises!",
